Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:34.45,CMTS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}註：指第五太陽紀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:10.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即將死亡的太陽高掛在所有國度上空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:24.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啟示錄曰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:34.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽第五度死亡之際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:40.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赤湖現於繼承舊都之名的新都之西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:46.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是第五位禦使降臨的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他是黑暗之鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,罪惡深重的黑羊之主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,盲目的白羊之王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:09.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為世界喚來暗黑時代者
Comment: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.23,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,酒 拿酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 為何本少爺要遭這種罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別晃來晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人怎麼飛得中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊準備好 下一發來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意 你個死光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有種解開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看我咬斷你的動脈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這把刀插進你嘴裏 看你還嘴不嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚 不要不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:47.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我幫你收拾屍體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你們是傭兵團我才跟隨過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹的事情跟流氓地痞有什麼區別?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想仗劍立名!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 這種事情我幹不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別囂張 你個臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為說出這種話之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還能平安走出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生 混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個就料理你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你擋住我的路了 能讓一讓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?你這是跟誰說...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混球 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,店家 引起騷動 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩幫我加滿水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一瓶拉姆酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:01.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救人要救到底啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這個好像很重的物件是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫巴克 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本是某個旅遊藝人團的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但被那群盜賊襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之後又是被關進鷯哥籠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又是被泡在酒瓶裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能活下來簡直不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:35.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,附近應該有很多那群盜賊的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其中不乏能手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不趕緊逃走的話會出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別唧唧歪歪個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 可能迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不坐上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚如此大雨很難上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我家女兒也希望你坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我這是為你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我被惡靈...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...纏身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 那可真是麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有神靈庇佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有幸運的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 坐上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的假肢男啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的強得跟怪物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才叫回了30個能手待命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能收拾他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 就沒有好點的集合地點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:43.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:49.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶以前是邪教徒信仰森之精靈的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:54.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他們將人的腸子挖出來繞樹一週褂起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以此作為供奉的活物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是其中的一棵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別開這種奇怪的玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:07.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方本來就很陰森了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傳言這個森林...還有怪物出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個世道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都是戰爭 天災
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,屍體隨處可見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對手可能就是魑魅魍魎這一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 是我先坐上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒資格抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不介意的話請嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我家自釀的葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:44.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:48.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚 危機四伏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要浪費別人的好意啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要就給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...這是打仗留下的創傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被惡靈咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:06.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 別嚇著我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫歌列特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:17.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你背上那個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:17.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 剛才酒館的事情我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不贊成使用暴力危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但救下了精靈這一點值得肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看你不像壞人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是傭兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎麼敢恭維呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...以殺人為生的行當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是為了救人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能輕易殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我討厭和尚的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:58.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的侄兒也說過要憑手中劍來揚名立萬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前在戰場上丟了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至死也是無名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若還在世 應已成家立室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,過上相應的幸福日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:16.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他是為了追求理想而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他是幸福的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過死了的話便一切休提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 請讓我睡一會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋一下 不然會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等...怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夢魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人做惡夢産生恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後以之為食的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說惡靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那你說的一切...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信神靈的存在 卻不相信惡靈的存在?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何發生這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是它喚來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烙印?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:42.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夢魔誕生自人類屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶曾是古老的戰場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,惡靈會上屍體的身襲擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夢魔出現 說明可能有更可怕的東西在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜 安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快點坐回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,歌列特!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是逃跑比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想走你自己走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:55.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,數量這麼多 你會死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這場面我見得多了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要說那是一把劍 可也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大 寬厚 沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直...就是鐵塊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呿 結果只有20人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:06.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人就一個 足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,派你們來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼鬼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:28.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:54.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你當火柴我也嫌你太潮濕!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是...你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,捲入他人的鬥爭而死去的傢伙是雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若連自己的命也無法自由掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人沒有保護自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無法抵擋我帶來的災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若介意會踩死螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的 你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都會跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠糾纏著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠盯著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的血肉 骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:54.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵 眼睛 心臟!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你的心臟!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要烙印還在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 只要那個烙印還在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會讓你逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你都是屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的憤怒 悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的恐懼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...全部屬於我們!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...格斯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:54.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於追上你了 黑色劍士!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:04.36,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 我忙著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:11.84,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
